description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 80, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 2 for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [80 Votes, Common]
